name: Satyr and Faun LoRA
description:
WHY IS IT SO GOOD ON REV ANIMATED?!

Based on satyrs and fauns from greek/roman mythology,

needed some satyr/fauns in my life so here we have it. works specially well for long legs, if you are getting to many thigh high looking legs try using pants/brown pants in the prompt,

Example training prompts:

  • Solo, male, Satyr, Faun, horns, pointy ears, hooves, loincloth, satchel, staff, long hair, white hair, forest background

  • Solo, female, Satyr, Faun, horns, animal ears, hooves, fur shirt, gloves, long hair, gray hair, small breasts, tail, book, skirt, butterflies, empty background, white background

  • Realistic, Photograph,Solo, female, Satyr, Faun, horns, hooves, brown shirt, necklace, gloves, long hair, staff, white hair,dreadlocks, small breasts, trees, forest background

  • solo, female, satyr, faun, hooves, horns, necklace, pointy ears, brown hair, long hair, sword, white shirt, sleeves, grey background, empty background

Made two, versions. both using same dataset and prompts, different settings, Satyr using 512x512 at 15 epochs, the other (Faun) using 752x752 for 10 epochs,

DONT MIND THE NAMES, the prompt satyr and faun are practically the same.
````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````

if you REALLY want the other epochs for better testing,(i honestly hate the testing part)
i've gathered all of them in these hugging-face repositories with training config and sample outputs, (not really too important)

512x512 - https://huggingface.co/BakingBeans/SatyrFaun/tree/main/SatyrFaun

752x752 - https://huggingface.co/BakingBeans/SatyrFaun-768/tree/main/SatyrTrained

IF USING HUGGING FACE FILES PLEASE BE AWARE THAT ALL FILES ARE NAMED THE SAME, PLEASE RENAME PROPERLY WHEN DOWNLOADING FOR YOUR USE
